spec_data.Name: python2-lazr-delegates
spec_data.Description:
The lazr.delegates package makes it easy to write objects that delegate
behavior to another object. The new object adds some property or behavior on
to the other object, while still providing the underlying interface, and
delegating behavior.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 11 Aug 2017 11:28:16 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Easily write objects that delegate behavior
